 p7zip-full provides 7z and 7za which handles more compression formats.

Package: p7zip-full
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Conflicts: p7zip (<< 4.39-1)
Replaces: p7zip (<< 4.39-1)
Suggests:
Description: 7-Zip is a file archiver with high compression ratio
 7-Zip is the file archiver that archives with the highest compression
 ratios. The program supports 7z (that implements LZMA compression
 algorithm), ZIP, Zip64, CAB, RAR, ARJ, GZIP, BZIP2, TAR, CPIO, RPM, ISO
 and DEB formats. Compression ratios with the new 7z format are 30 to 50%
 better than ratios with the ZIP format.
